OL,3,C'I shouldn't have done what I did'
OL,4,CDaniel Khalife admits escaping prison
OL,6,FDaniel Khalife has told a court he
OL,7,Fescaped from prison so he would be
OL,8,Fkept in a high security unit away from
OL,9,F"sex offenders" and "terrorists" who
OL,10,Fwanted to harm him.
OL,12,FThe former soldier, 23, is alleged to
OL,13,Fhave escaped from HMP Wandsworth by
OL,14,Ftying himself to the underside of a
OL,15,Ffood delivery truck using bedsheets in
OL,16,FSeptember 2023.
