OL,4,CDaniel Khalife admits escaping prison
OL,6,FAfter being taken to Wandsworth prison
OL,7,Fin January 2023, he was told he would
OL,8,Fbe kept on a wing for vulnerable
OL,9,Fprisoners because there were
OL,10,F"terrorist offenders" at Wandsworth
OL,11,Fwho "want to kill you", the court
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FKhalife told jurors that "95%" of
OL,15,Fthose in the unit were "serious sex
OL,16,Foffenders, rapists, paedophiles, that
OL,17,Fsort of thing".
OL,19,FHe said: "It was not a nice place to
OL,20,Fbe ... people on that wing said
OL,21,Fstrange things to me."
