OL,3,C'I shouldn't have done what I did'
OL,4,CDaniel Khalife admits escaping prison
OL,6,FAfter a "show" escape was not reported
OL,7,Fto senior prison staff, Khalife
OL,8,Fdecided escaping for real was the only
OL,9,Fway to guarantee being kept in the
OL,10,Fhigh security unit, the court heard.
OL,12,FThe former soldier told the court that
OL,13,Fbefore his successful escape, he
OL,14,F"acted suspiciously" around the food
OL,15,Fdelivery lorry and was spotted by
OL,16,Fkitchen staff.
OL,18,FBut Khalife was "pretty shocked" when
OL,19,Fthe matter was not escalated to senior
OL,20,Fprison officers, and he faced no
OL,21,Fconsequences, the court heard.
