OL,6,FHe then decided escaping for real was
OL,7,Fhis only option, the court heard.
OL,9,FFive days before his successful escape
OL,10,Fhe attached a sling to the underside
OL,11,Fof the lorry made from "kitchen
OL,12,Ftrousers" and carabiners, the court
OL,13,Fwas told.
OL,15,FThe sling "wasn't spotted at
OL,16,FWandsworth gate or any other prison",
OL,17,Fhe said.
OL,19,F"When the tail lift raised it covered
OL,20,Fme entirely.
