OL,4,CDaniel Khalife admits escaping prison
OL,6,FAfter absconding from his barracks,
OL,7,FKhalife lived in a van in the nearby
OL,8,Ftown of Stone for 25 days, "trying not
OL,9,Fto freeze to death", he said.
